name: Cheese Quake
description: Cheese Quake by TGA Subcool Seeds is a 60/40 indica-dominant cross between Cheese and Querkle.  A hint of grape is detectable, but its aroma is led by the funky sour aroma commonly associated with Cheese hybrids. Expect to feel tingy invigoration followed by uplifting body sensations to help you feel relaxed and carefree.
